	<h3 class="panel-title">Admissions</h3>
</div>
<div class="panel-body">

 	<h4>Admission to NTC is open to:</h4>
	
  <ul>
	  <li>Members of Newlife Christian Center Alabang</li>
	  <li>Newlife satellite churches and affiliates,</li>
	  <li>Born-again Christian believers from other churches, both national and international.</li>
	</ul>
  
 	<h4>Admission Requirements:</h4>

	<h5>Day School (Full-time and Pastoral Track)</h5>
  <ul>
	  <li>Online application form</li>
	  <li>Scanned Pastoral Recommendation</li>
	  <li>Scanned Commitment to Honor Form</li>
	  <li>Scanned NBI Clearance (issued within 3 months prior to enrollment)</li>
	  <li>Scanned Medical clearance (issued within 3 months prior to enrollment)</li>
	  <li>Interview</li>
	  <li>Training Fee: Php 1,800.00 monthly</li>
	</ul>
  
	<h5>International Students</h5>
  <ul>
	  <li>Would be required to show proof of legal permission to reside and/or study in the Philippines</li>
	  <li>Online application form</li>
	  <li>Scanned Pastoral Recommendation</li>
	  <li>Scanned Commitment to Honor Form</li>
	  <li>Scanned NBI Clearance (issued within 3 months prior to enrollment)</li>
	  <li>Scanned Medical clearance (issued within 3 months prior to enrollment)</li>
	  <li>Interview</li>
	  <li>Training Fee: Php 1,800.00 monthly</li>
	</ul>
  
  <span class="label label-important"><strong>Note:</strong> All international students bear the sole responsibility for compliance to Philippine immigration requirements. NTC is not responsible for monthly expenses, including food and lodging.</span>
  
	<h5>Blockweek Nights @ NTC</h5>
  <ul>
	  <li>Training Fee: PHP 400.00 per subject</li>
	</ul>
  
  <span class="label label-important">
  * For NCC Alabang staff: NBI and Medical clearances are not required <br />
	** NTC and its programs are not recognized by any Philippine educational regulatory body.
